00:11:53,150 --> 00:11:55,195
a man you admire so much.

367
00:11:55,239 --> 00:11:57,806
- What? So all this
was just to make me mad?

368
00:11:57,850 --> 00:12:00,331
- I need you to feel
the anger and resentment

369
00:12:00,374 --> 00:12:04,639
that Tyrone McCallister feels
every single day of his life.

370
00:12:04,683 --> 00:12:06,728
- Who's Tyrone McCallister?

371
00:12:06,772 --> 00:12:08,165
- You are.

372
00:12:08,208 --> 00:12:11,037
