00:12:14,084 --> 00:12:15,389
and then expect them
to get on board.

376
00:12:15,433 --> 00:12:16,521
Right, Sarge?

377
00:12:16,564 --> 00:12:18,697
- Sarge?

378
00:12:18,740 --> 00:12:21,352
My name's Tyrone.

379
00:12:21,395 --> 00:12:22,701
Tyrone McGallagher.

380
00:12:22,744 --> 00:12:24,964
- McCallister.
- McCallister.

381
00:12:25,007 --> 00:12:26,705
