blood they've ever seen.

384
00:12:30,361 --> 00:12:31,971
- I knew this was all too good
to be true.

385
00:12:32,014 --> 00:12:33,581
Now David's gonna
clear his name

386
00:12:33,625 --> 00:12:36,062
and singlehandedly take down
drug dealers and dirty cops

